    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m looking for a new home for my trusty ride. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super reliable for me. I\u2019ve taken great care of it, and honestly, it still drives like a dream! It\u2019s perfect if you\u2019re looking for a dependable car without the 'brand new' price tag. Come take it for a spin\u2014you\u2019re going to love how it handles!",
