      "description": "We are pleased to present this exceptionally maintained vehicle, offering a refined driving experience and proven mechanical reliability. This automobile has been curated for the discerning owner who values both performance and aesthetic integrity. It features a well-appointed interior and a robust powertrain that has been subject to rigorous standards of care. This offering represents a premier opportunity to acquire a sophisticated vehicle that performs with distinction and remains in commendable standing. We invite you to experience the caliber of this motorcar firsthand.",
      "price": 34800.0,
