    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s ready for your next adventure? I\u2019m parting with my trusty car, and it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really nice shape, runs super smoothly, and has been well-loved over the years. It's perfect for daily commutes or those fun weekend getaways! I\u2019ve taken great care of it, and I\u2019m sure you\u2019ll love it as much as I have. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
      "price": 29500.0,
