    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver-focused example featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, characterized by its six individual throttle bodies and recent VANOS overhaul for precise valve timing. The drivetrain is anchored by a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and an M Variable Differential Lock, providing exceptional mechanical grip. The chassis remains rigid with proactive subframe reinforcement already completed, ensuring structural integrity under high lateral loads. Suspension components maintain factory-spec kinematics, offering the communicative steering feel and balanced damping profile essential for this platform. This is a mechanically sorted machine ready for spirited canyon runs or track day duties.",
